_sText:
Aim_bunker_v1 is my very first map created with the hammer editor.
It's a very dark underground map which reqiures the cvar mp_flashlight set to 1 if you want to be able to see anything.
Two spawning areas, CT and T, each with 26 spawnpoints. Buyzones covering the whole spawning areas. 3 exits from each spawning area leading to a middle room.
Any tips and ideas for future versions would be greatly appreciated. Other general mapping tips aswell. Thanks.
